14 (2) Other members of the Consortium who are not otherwise
15 compensated by their employer shall be entitled to per diem compensation and
16 reimbursement of expenses as permitted under 32 V.S.A. § 1010 for not more
17 than five meetings in fiscal year 2026.
18 (3) The payments under this subsection shall be made from monies
19 appropriated by the General Assembly.
